name: Hinata Hyuuga (Shippuden, The Last [Emo Hinata], Boruto)
description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

for those that want to copy and paste the prompts you have to switch <lora:HinataV3:1> to <lora:hinataHyuugaShippudenThe_v1Epoch3:1> (i would suggest renaming the Lora)

Lora of Hinata from Naruto (Shippuden, The Last: Naruto the Movie, and Boruto) (war outfit isn't included yet).

weights 0.6 - 1

struggles with the fishnet top.

tags for different versions

jacket: hyuuga hinata, Hinata-Jacket-Outfit (optional: purple_jacket, blue-pants, fishnet_top).

sleeveless: hyuuga hinata, Hinata-Sleeveless-Outfit, (recommended: sleeveless_shirt, black_shorts, bandaged_leg).

Emo: hyuuga hinata, Emo-Hinata, (recommended: black_lips, eye_shadow).

Boruto: hyuuga hinata, Hinata-Boruto-Outfit, purple_cropped_jacket, white_undershirt, green_shorts, (optional: short_hair).

Optional tags: grey_eyes, white_eyes, purple_eyes, byakugan.

using a tagger and using that as a prompt can give pretty good results.

noticed I forgot to take nsfw out of the prompts, was annoyed it kept showing her boobs lol
